[0m[49m[39m  369, 369[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  370, 370[0m:[39m[49m ### Expected Results
[0m[49m[39m  371, 371[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  372, 372[0m:[39m[49m **Sample prediction output:**
